[Princess's Mansion]

6
00:01:39,340 --> 00:01:39,980
It's okay.

7
00:01:40,580 --> 00:01:43,020
Miss Qin, I'm back.

8
00:01:43,900 --> 00:01:46,060
Why didn't you tell me you came back?

9
00:01:49,820 --> 00:01:51,940
There happened to be
my sister's wedding.

10
00:01:52,380 --> 00:01:54,700
I was thinking about going to you
once it's over.

11
00:01:58,180 --> 00:01:58,980
Miss Qin,

12
00:01:59,860 --> 00:02:01,940
everything in the army is under control.

13
00:02:02,380 --> 00:02:04,420
You can rest assured.
Your brother is all right.

14
00:02:06,860 --> 00:02:08,460
You came back

15
00:02:09,260 --> 00:02:10,540
a little steadier this time.

16
00:02:13,580 --> 00:02:14,260
By the way,

17
00:02:18,420 --> 00:02:20,820
this is the jade I brought back
from the border.

18
00:02:21,780 --> 00:02:24,140
I had craftsmen carve it into this.

19
00:02:25,460 --> 00:02:26,460
I want to give it to you.

20
00:02:28,020 --> 00:02:28,900
Do you like it?

21
00:02:32,260 --> 00:02:33,380
I thought you were steadier.

22
00:02:33,620 --> 00:02:35,020
You are playing with these toys again.

23
00:02:37,540 --> 00:02:39,900
Come and tell me about the battlefield.

24
00:02:40,140 --> 00:02:40,700
Let's go.

25
00:02:41,300 --> 00:02:42,620
You bathed quickly.

26
00:03:12,700 --> 00:03:15,500
Mrs. Pei, you're in bed.

27
00:03:15,500 --> 00:03:16,580
Where am I supposed to sleep?

28
00:03:16,580 --> 00:03:19,860
You can sleep wherever you like.
I'm too sleepy.

29
00:03:47,460 --> 00:03:49,660
Why don't you come to bed, too?

30
00:03:56,300 --> 00:03:57,580
That's not appropriate.

31
00:03:58,860 --> 00:04:00,620
Then forget about it.

32
00:04:00,620 --> 00:04:01,820
You can sleep where you like.

33
00:04:02,180 --> 00:04:03,060
Wait. You...

34
00:04:13,940 --> 00:04:16,620
Many eyes are on us on this wedding day.

35
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:21,660
If I go out looking for a quilt,

36
00:04:22,580 --> 00:04:24,180
is it not appropriate?

37
00:04:29,420 --> 00:04:31,060
But I'll freeze to death sleeping here.

38
00:04:32,980 --> 00:04:33,660
Whatever!

39
00:04:35,900 --> 00:04:37,620
Oh, I almost forgot...

40
00:04:41,700 --> 00:04:42,300
Come back.

41
00:04:45,020 --> 00:04:45,860
Come over.

42
00:04:48,460 --> 00:04:49,620
Confess to me.

43
00:04:50,140 --> 00:04:52,180
What does Your Highness
want me to confess?

44
00:04:52,540 --> 00:04:53,900
Tell me the truth.

45
00:04:54,420 --> 00:04:57,060
Why did Su Rongqing come
to escort me today?

46
00:04:58,900 --> 00:05:01,300
I thought Your Highness
had something special to say.

47
00:05:04,860 --> 00:05:08,180
After all, this is
Your Highness's wedding day.

48
00:05:08,620 --> 00:05:10,700
I was just trying
to please Your Highness.

49
00:05:11,780 --> 00:05:13,020
To please me?

50
00:05:14,060 --> 00:05:15,260
Did you do that on purpose?

51
00:05:15,860 --> 00:05:18,020
You knew I was killed by Su Rongqing.

52
00:05:18,020 --> 00:05:19,420
Yet you asked him to pick me up.

53
00:05:19,540 --> 00:05:20,540
Were you humiliating me?

54
00:05:20,820 --> 00:05:22,860
Why does that sound so bad
coming from you?

55
00:05:23,620 --> 00:05:25,620
Am I that type of person
in your opinion?

56
00:05:25,740 --> 00:05:27,140
In my opinion...

57
00:05:29,980 --> 00:05:34,020
In my opinion, you're a saint.
A real gentleman.

58
00:05:34,420 --> 00:05:35,460
You're being a...

59
00:05:37,380 --> 00:05:38,420
I won't argue with you.

60
00:05:42,340 --> 00:05:43,380
I was thinking

61
00:05:44,180 --> 00:05:46,900
Your Highness's relationship
with Su Rongqing didn't work last time.

62
00:05:47,380 --> 00:05:49,740
Then maybe you can start over this time.

63
00:05:53,580 --> 00:05:55,020
Why do I have to start it over?

64
00:05:55,420 --> 00:05:56,140
Why?

65
00:05:57,060 --> 00:05:59,260
Don't you still care about Su Rongqing?

66
00:06:05,620 --> 00:06:06,260
Never mind.

67
00:06:07,300 --> 00:06:09,060
I would be lying to say I don't care.

68
00:06:10,060 --> 00:06:11,060
However,

69
00:06:12,580 --> 00:06:13,820
you and I are married now.

70
00:06:13,820 --> 00:06:15,580
It doesn't make any sense anymore.

71
00:06:25,340 --> 00:06:26,180
I know

72
00:06:27,140 --> 00:06:29,740
you're afraid Su Rongqing
will remain the same,

73
00:06:30,180 --> 00:06:31,420
putting power before you

74
00:06:31,420 --> 00:06:32,580
and his family before you.

75
00:06:34,700 --> 00:06:37,100
You say you understand him
and don't blame him.

76
00:06:37,260 --> 00:06:38,340
But is that true?

77
00:06:39,340 --> 00:06:41,180
If Your Highness really don't blame him,

78
00:06:41,180 --> 00:06:43,020
why not choose him from the start?

79
00:06:50,540 --> 00:06:51,860
I'll be honest with you.

80
00:06:52,780 --> 00:06:55,780
I talked with Su Rongqing
before the wedding.

81
00:06:57,220 --> 00:06:58,100
I asked him

82
00:06:58,940 --> 00:07:01,420
if the wife conflicted with the family,

83
00:07:01,820 --> 00:07:02,900
who would he choose?

84
00:07:04,980 --> 00:07:07,940
I side with whoever is right.

85
00:07:09,620 --> 00:07:10,740
Mr. Su made a good point.

86
00:07:10,740 --> 00:07:11,900
I'll take my leave.

87
00:07:14,100 --> 00:07:14,780
Mr. Su.

88
00:07:14,780 --> 00:07:17,180
[Censorate]

89
00:07:17,180 --> 00:07:18,980
Mr. Pei, what else do you need?

90
00:07:19,700 --> 00:07:21,300
I still have one favour to ask.

91
00:07:23,060 --> 00:07:25,700
I'm sure you know
about my family situation.

92
00:07:27,020 --> 00:07:30,260
On the day of the wedding,
I don't want them to do anything.

93
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:33,420
So I dare ask you
to pick up the bride for me.

94
00:07:35,260 --> 00:07:37,300
Mr. Pei, you're joking.

95
00:07:40,300 --> 00:07:41,820
Su, you should know

96
00:07:42,140 --> 00:07:44,340
the princess marrying me is expedient.

97
00:07:44,820 --> 00:07:46,020
The wedding of me and the princess is

98
00:07:46,180 --> 00:07:47,500
just a deal.

99
00:07:48,300 --> 00:07:49,060
Then...

100
00:07:50,860 --> 00:07:51,980
Why me?

101
00:07:55,180 --> 00:07:56,180
I think

102
00:07:57,220 --> 00:07:58,940
Su, you want to protect the princess.

103
00:08:03,460 --> 00:08:05,300
But what identity should I use
when picking her up?

104
00:08:09,580 --> 00:08:11,260
How about my sworn brother?

105
00:08:12,740 --> 00:08:14,740
My greetings, sworn brother.

106
00:08:18,180 --> 00:08:18,980
So,

107
00:08:19,180 --> 00:08:21,420
Su Rongqing is
not who Your Highness think he is.

108
00:08:21,980 --> 00:08:23,500
He still cares about you.

109
00:08:27,260 --> 00:08:29,100
And don't feel old all the time.

110
00:08:30,220 --> 00:08:32,100
You look like you're eighteen now.

111
00:08:32,220 --> 00:08:33,340
At such a young age,

112
00:08:33,340 --> 00:08:34,740
why do you refuse all the possibilities

113
00:08:34,740 --> 00:08:35,740
so easily?

114
00:08:41,140 --> 00:08:42,100
Let me ask you something.

115
00:08:43,100 --> 00:08:45,140
When Su Rongqing came to pick you up,

116
00:08:45,220 --> 00:08:46,740
did you really not think about

117
00:08:46,740 --> 00:08:47,980
marrying him for a moment?

118
00:08:54,940 --> 00:08:56,180
Why should I tell you that?

119
00:08:57,900 --> 00:08:59,820
To begin with,
I don't know if what you just said is

120
00:08:59,940 --> 00:09:01,660
true or not.

121
00:09:02,260 --> 00:09:03,380
Even if it's true,

122
00:09:03,380 --> 00:09:05,100
we're married now.

123
00:09:05,620 --> 00:09:07,180
One day when we'll be apart,

124
00:09:07,340 --> 00:09:08,860
even as a princess,

125
00:09:08,980 --> 00:09:10,060
the Su Family won't allow him

126
00:09:10,060 --> 00:09:11,660
to marry a divorced woman.

127
00:09:11,780 --> 00:09:12,780
Rest assured.

128
00:09:13,220 --> 00:09:15,620
I have drawn up a plan
for Your Highness.

129
00:09:16,820 --> 00:09:17,420
Wait here.

130
00:09:18,940 --> 00:09:20,100
[Eastern Palace]
Young Master Qin

131
00:09:20,300 --> 00:09:23,260
cut three enemy generals
off their horses.

132
00:09:23,940 --> 00:09:25,660
The enemy troops lost faith.

133
00:09:25,660 --> 00:09:27,460
We pursued with victory.

134
00:09:28,260 --> 00:09:30,220
By the time we reached the canyon,

135
00:09:30,420 --> 00:09:31,500
there was a whistle.

136
00:09:31,820 --> 00:09:32,580
Ambush?

137
00:09:34,260 --> 00:09:34,860
What happened later?

138
00:09:34,860 --> 00:09:36,700
How did you fight your way out?

139
00:09:38,100 --> 00:09:41,180
Well, I need to tell you in detail.

140
00:09:53,500 --> 00:09:54,780
This plan has

141
00:09:54,820 --> 00:09:55,860
four steps.

142
00:09:56,420 --> 00:09:58,500
The first step is to know yourself.

143
00:09:58,820 --> 00:10:01,300
Your Highness must first
make your position clear.

144
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:03,860
Figure out what your feelings
for Su Rongqing are.

145
00:10:04,100 --> 00:10:05,740
Secondly, to know your enemy.

146
00:10:06,140 --> 00:10:07,380
We need to find out

147
00:10:07,460 --> 00:10:09,100
what Su Rongqing's feelings for you are.

148
00:10:09,820 --> 00:10:10,860
Leave that to me.

149
00:10:11,500 --> 00:10:13,820
I will make good relations
with Su Rongqing in advance.

150
00:10:14,100 --> 00:10:16,100
The third step is
to encourage the enemy.

151
00:10:16,620 --> 00:10:18,900
We must let Su Rongqing know

152
00:10:19,100 --> 00:10:20,900
Your Highness and I are only allies.

153
00:10:21,060 --> 00:10:22,700
He still has a chance.

154
00:10:23,660 --> 00:10:24,460
The fourth step is

155
00:10:24,460 --> 00:10:25,940
the most important step.

156
00:10:26,020 --> 00:10:26,820
To capture the enemy.

157
00:10:27,180 --> 00:10:29,540
I will create some opportunities

158
00:10:29,820 --> 00:10:31,620
for you and Su Rongqing

159
00:10:31,860 --> 00:10:34,220
so that things can happen
between you and Su Rongqing.

160
00:10:34,740 --> 00:10:35,860
With your capability,

161
00:10:36,100 --> 00:10:37,340
Su Rongqing should be

162
00:10:37,500 --> 00:10:38,820
captured by you easily.

163
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:45,300
You really have me covered.

164
00:10:48,460 --> 00:10:50,300
I don't have you covered.

165
00:10:51,540 --> 00:10:53,980
With your face, your figure,

166
00:10:54,100 --> 00:10:55,580
your temper, and personality,

167
00:10:55,620 --> 00:10:56,860
all men in the world

168
00:10:56,860 --> 00:10:58,100
will be yours,

169
00:10:58,340 --> 00:10:59,220
if you want.

170
00:11:00,980 --> 00:11:03,100
Su Rongqing is just another man.
Is it difficult?

171
00:11:04,220 --> 00:11:07,220
You've been talking a lot.

172
00:11:07,420 --> 00:11:08,500
Is that all true?

173
00:11:08,660 --> 00:11:09,700
I'm going to believe it.

174
00:11:10,140 --> 00:11:12,060
You don't have to believe me,

175
00:11:12,460 --> 00:11:14,620
but Your Highness must
believe in yourself.

176
00:11:18,060 --> 00:11:18,740
Yeah.

177
00:11:19,900 --> 00:11:23,140
What you just said
makes perfect sense to me.

178
00:11:23,860 --> 00:11:26,020
It was like a wakening call to me.

179
00:11:26,780 --> 00:11:27,740
How about this?

180
00:11:27,860 --> 00:11:29,540
Since you've thought about
so much for me,

181
00:11:29,740 --> 00:11:30,780
starting from today,

182
00:11:30,820 --> 00:11:32,260
I'll work for your marriage, too.

183
00:11:32,980 --> 00:11:34,020
You and Miss Qin

184
00:11:34,020 --> 00:11:35,500
were separated by fate then.

185
00:11:35,500 --> 00:11:36,820
Now you have another chance.

186
00:11:36,940 --> 00:11:39,100
Don't you want to muster up the courage
to go after her?

187
00:11:39,500 --> 00:11:40,260
No need.

188
00:11:40,260 --> 00:11:41,100
Miss Qin and I were...

189
00:11:41,100 --> 00:11:42,060
How can that be?

190
00:11:42,100 --> 00:11:43,220
You thought so much for me.

191
00:11:43,220 --> 00:11:44,820
How can I not make plans for you?

192
00:11:45,060 --> 00:11:45,580
No, I...

193
00:11:45,620 --> 00:11:46,580
If you keep rejecting me,

194
00:11:46,580 --> 00:11:47,860
I will start wondering

195
00:11:47,860 --> 00:11:50,260
what your real purpose is
setting me up with Su Rongqing.

196
00:11:53,660 --> 00:11:54,980
Your Highness have a point.

197
00:11:55,420 --> 00:11:56,860
It's just
that the most important thing now is

198
00:11:56,940 --> 00:11:58,340
Your Highness's relationship
with Su Rongqing.

199
00:11:58,340 --> 00:12:00,140
Miss Qin and I can wait.

200
00:12:00,300 --> 00:12:02,900
Then Su Rongqing and I can also wait.

201
00:12:04,500 --> 00:12:05,220
Fine.

202
00:12:05,660 --> 00:12:06,540
Then go to sleep.

203
00:12:19,820 --> 00:12:21,500
You need to stop wandering around.

204
00:12:21,740 --> 00:12:22,820
Sleep here,

205
00:12:23,820 --> 00:12:24,980
so no one finds out.

206
00:12:41,860 --> 00:12:43,940
You and I are really funny.

207
00:12:45,180 --> 00:12:48,420
Twenty years of ups and downs.

208
00:12:49,940 --> 00:12:52,780
We are a couple, but not a real couple.

209
00:12:53,580 --> 00:12:54,620
We are allies,

210
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:57,540
but not exactly real allies.

211
00:12:58,820 --> 00:13:00,340
We tease each other,

212
00:13:00,420 --> 00:13:02,140
while wanting the best for each other.

213
00:13:03,420 --> 00:13:04,860
I'm sure there's no one like you,

214
00:13:05,180 --> 00:13:06,300
on the wedding day,

215
00:13:06,620 --> 00:13:08,380
making plans
for the bride's relationship

216
00:13:08,380 --> 00:13:09,780
with someone else.

217
00:13:11,860 --> 00:13:13,740
What kind of relationship
do you think we have?

218
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:15,940
Didn't I tell you?

219
00:13:16,540 --> 00:13:17,700
I was hoping

220
00:13:17,820 --> 00:13:21,060
Your Highness could be happier
on your wedding day.

221
00:13:26,580 --> 00:13:28,300
If Your Highness think well of me,

222
00:13:28,420 --> 00:13:30,420
you can think of me as a brother.

223
00:13:30,740 --> 00:13:31,420
Don't.

224
00:13:32,220 --> 00:13:33,980
I don't have a hobby
of getting brothers.

225
00:13:36,220 --> 00:13:37,140
Then suit yourself.

226
00:13:38,380 --> 00:13:39,460
However,

227
00:13:41,940 --> 00:13:44,100
you and I should be able
to count as best friends

228
00:13:44,300 --> 00:13:45,620
by now.

229
00:13:50,780 --> 00:13:51,620
Besties?

230
00:13:52,420 --> 00:13:53,220
What do you think?

231
00:13:53,420 --> 00:13:54,140
No.

232
00:13:56,860 --> 00:13:57,540
Bestie.

233
00:13:58,380 --> 00:13:59,340
Bestie, my bestie.

234
00:13:59,340 --> 00:14:00,860
Okay, stop. Don't gross me out.

235
00:14:03,420 --> 00:14:05,180
Good night, my bestie.

236
00:14:15,460 --> 00:14:16,420
Dawn breaks.

237
00:14:20,100 --> 00:14:22,620
I was too focused
on talking about the war.

238
00:14:22,740 --> 00:14:24,700
I didn't notice
it had been a whole night.

239
00:14:25,220 --> 00:14:26,420
It's my fault.

240
00:14:26,420 --> 00:14:27,100
No. No.

241
00:14:27,820 --> 00:14:29,820
I was just too involved
in the conversation.

242
00:14:32,380 --> 00:14:35,220
Since my father died in the war
and I stayed in the capital,

243
00:14:36,060 --> 00:14:38,820
it's been five years
away from the border.

244
00:14:39,060 --> 00:14:41,660
Don't blame me
if I talked a little too much.

245
00:14:42,580 --> 00:14:44,540
I'll take my leave soon,

246
00:14:44,940 --> 00:14:47,300
so as not to let people walk in
and be misunderstood.

247
00:14:48,140 --> 00:14:48,980
That's all right.

248
00:14:49,940 --> 00:14:51,100
If you still want to hear it,

249
00:14:51,140 --> 00:14:52,660
I'll just keep telling you more.

250
00:14:53,740 --> 00:14:56,180
One day we can go to war together.

251
00:14:56,340 --> 00:14:58,940
Miss Qin can also find a place
to show your martial arts.

252
00:15:02,140 --> 00:15:04,620
Huajing ladies think
being thin is beautiful.

253
00:15:05,060 --> 00:15:07,540
People practicing martial arts
for years like me are

254
00:15:07,580 --> 00:15:10,260
often accused
of being vulgar and indecent.

255
00:15:11,100 --> 00:15:13,540
Do you also think so?

256
00:15:15,140 --> 00:15:16,060
Of course, not.

257
00:15:17,300 --> 00:15:18,900
Speaking of being brave and valiant,

258
00:15:19,340 --> 00:15:21,220
there is only one person in Huajing.

259
00:15:21,380 --> 00:15:22,180
Who is that?

260
00:15:23,020 --> 00:15:24,620
Qin Zhenzhen.

261
00:15:30,620 --> 00:15:33,020
The Crown Prince is
sure to be reassuring.

262
00:15:34,660 --> 00:15:36,660
I'm leaving. See you later.

263
00:15:39,540 --> 00:15:40,340
Miss Qin,

264
00:15:42,020 --> 00:15:44,700
I'll let the porter
escort you out the back.

265
00:15:45,140 --> 00:15:47,580
If you want to see me, don't fly around.

266
00:15:47,980 --> 00:15:49,780
The guards around me are experts.

267
00:15:50,700 --> 00:15:52,340
I wouldn't want my people

268
00:15:52,380 --> 00:15:54,020
to hurt each other.

269
00:15:54,540 --> 00:15:56,140
Who are your people?

270
00:15:56,900 --> 00:15:58,780
General Qin is like a brother to me.

271
00:15:59,580 --> 00:16:01,180
Of course, you're my people.

272
00:16:06,900 --> 00:16:08,820
Then I'm leaving.

273
00:16:09,220 --> 00:16:10,100
I'll walk you out.

274
00:16:10,100 --> 00:16:11,780
