Lately, Queen Mother has been

275
00:16:11,780 --> 00:16:13,500
talking about making Shangguan Ya
the Crown Princess.

276
00:16:13,700 --> 00:16:15,460
I just want to ask her what she thinks.

277
00:16:16,460 --> 00:16:17,660
You can rest assured.

278
00:16:18,100 --> 00:16:19,940
I know Shangguan Ya very well.

279
00:16:20,340 --> 00:16:22,900
There were only a few places
she used to go.

280
00:16:23,140 --> 00:16:24,100
If she isn't home,

281
00:16:24,220 --> 00:16:26,140
she must be at some tea party
or poetry club.

282
00:16:26,140 --> 00:16:26,940
She's easy to find.

283
00:16:28,780 --> 00:16:29,420
Your Highness,

284
00:16:29,700 --> 00:16:30,540
sorry for the inconvenience.

285
00:16:31,220 --> 00:16:33,860
My lady was invited
by the Jiwen Poetry Society today

286
00:16:34,420 --> 00:16:35,700
and has been off to the tea party.

287
00:16:35,820 --> 00:16:37,140
She is at the Jiwen Poetry Society.

288
00:16:37,140 --> 00:16:38,660
I'll just go looking for her.

289
00:16:38,740 --> 00:16:40,420
Your Highness, please suit yourself.

290
00:16:40,780 --> 00:16:42,580
Call me if you need anything.

291
00:16:44,100 --> 00:16:45,180
What did I say?

292
00:16:49,620 --> 00:16:50,740
Do you know her well?

293
00:16:51,380 --> 00:16:52,460
Of course.

294
00:16:53,980 --> 00:16:55,660
After she married
into the Eastern Palace in the past,

295
00:16:56,340 --> 00:16:58,780
we spent a lot of time together.
I know her well.

296
00:17:00,140 --> 00:17:01,340
You know her well?

297
00:17:01,940 --> 00:17:03,340
I wonder what Your Highness think

298
00:17:03,540 --> 00:17:04,820
she is like.

299
00:17:07,980 --> 00:17:09,900
We often talk together.

300
00:17:10,500 --> 00:17:13,220
She's a person who knows the rules.

301
00:17:13,460 --> 00:17:15,220
She has elegant taste
and graceful manners.

302
00:17:16,380 --> 00:17:17,820
Though,

303
00:17:19,420 --> 00:17:21,380
there were a few moments
when she was less elegant,

304
00:17:22,940 --> 00:17:24,140
overall,

305
00:17:24,580 --> 00:17:26,020
she's someone too focused on manners.

306
00:17:29,820 --> 00:17:31,260
[Jiwen Poetry Society]
Miss Shangguan?

307
00:17:31,740 --> 00:17:33,380
She didn't come here today.

308
00:17:35,660 --> 00:17:36,460
Didn't come?

309
00:17:37,020 --> 00:17:39,740
Since Miss Shangguan moved to Huajing,

310
00:17:40,140 --> 00:17:41,660
she's only come to the poetry club once.

311
00:17:46,820 --> 00:17:47,620
But

312
00:17:48,100 --> 00:17:49,980
Shangguan Ya said to me

313
00:17:50,380 --> 00:17:53,340
she used to be here
before she got married.

314
00:17:55,460 --> 00:17:56,540
Forget it.

315
00:17:57,180 --> 00:17:59,740
You're never a good judge of character.

316
00:18:02,820 --> 00:18:05,380
Today, the princess has urgent business
with Miss Shangguan.

317
00:18:05,460 --> 00:18:07,380
I wonder if you could do us a favour

318
00:18:07,580 --> 00:18:09,020
and tell us where Miss Shangguan

319
00:18:09,020 --> 00:18:10,340
likes to go normally.

320
00:18:16,900 --> 00:18:17,540
Come over.

321
00:18:21,820 --> 00:18:24,820
Miss Shangguan's whereabouts are
unknown to us.

322
00:18:24,900 --> 00:18:26,860
But I heard

323
00:18:26,860 --> 00:18:28,500
Miss Shangguan has been seen

324
00:18:28,500 --> 00:18:30,580
carrying a pass
to the Jucai House next door.

325
00:18:31,100 --> 00:18:33,020
You might want to look there.

326
00:18:36,140 --> 00:18:39,140
Ju... Jucai House?

327
00:18:39,380 --> 00:18:40,500
The gambling house?

328
00:18:41,700 --> 00:18:43,460
That girl must be lying.

329
00:18:43,740 --> 00:18:45,540
Shangguan Ya is
the most standard young lady

330
00:18:45,540 --> 00:18:46,660
of noble families.

331
00:18:46,660 --> 00:18:48,020
How could she go to a place like that?

332
00:18:48,020 --> 00:18:49,620
Impossible. Let's not waste time.

333
00:18:50,220 --> 00:18:52,180
We are already here.
There's no harm in a visit.

334
00:18:54,460 --> 00:18:55,340
Besides,

335
00:18:55,500 --> 00:18:57,660
fate gave us another chance.

336
00:18:58,180 --> 00:18:59,460
Shouldn't we

337
00:18:59,700 --> 00:19:01,420
see something different?

338
00:19:03,500 --> 00:19:06,660
[Qionghua Palace]
Do you know why I called you here?

339
00:19:07,620 --> 00:19:09,780
It's about choosing my wife.

340
00:19:10,260 --> 00:19:11,420
I'm glad you understand.

341
00:19:13,300 --> 00:19:14,900
I have promised your uncle

342
00:19:15,180 --> 00:19:17,860
to make Ya the Crown Princess.

343
00:19:20,180 --> 00:19:21,340
What do you think?

344
00:19:24,700 --> 00:19:26,540
Now that you have decided,

345
00:19:27,060 --> 00:19:28,220
why bother asking me?

346
00:19:28,940 --> 00:19:31,300
You don't like Ya?

347
00:19:31,780 --> 00:19:33,020
We've barely met before.

348
00:19:33,620 --> 00:19:36,700
There is no like or not like her.

349
00:19:37,060 --> 00:19:37,940
That's easy.

350
00:19:38,220 --> 00:19:40,900
I'll arrange for you to meet sometime.

351
00:19:42,700 --> 00:19:43,500
Queen Mother,

352
00:19:46,300 --> 00:19:48,620
can I not get married so soon?

353
00:19:51,340 --> 00:19:52,300
Is

354
00:19:53,700 --> 00:19:54,940
it up to us?

355
00:19:58,020 --> 00:19:59,340
I promise you

356
00:19:59,860 --> 00:20:02,060
if you make sure
Ya is the Crown Princess,

357
00:20:02,540 --> 00:20:05,100
I'll help you
with any other girl you like.

358
00:20:11,120 --> 00:20:13,750
[Jucai House]

359
00:20:17,780 --> 00:20:18,460
Open the door.

360
00:20:31,060 --> 00:20:33,100
How do you feel
being here for the first time?

361
00:20:35,100 --> 00:20:36,100
Do you come here a lot?

362
00:20:36,780 --> 00:20:37,780
I don't come here a lot.

363
00:20:39,980 --> 00:20:41,940
Full of smoke and mess.

364
00:20:41,940 --> 00:20:43,540
How could Shangguan Ya
come to a place like this?

365
00:20:43,540 --> 00:20:45,300
You know nothing. Just look.

366
00:20:54,140 --> 00:20:55,300
I never should have trusted you.

367
00:20:57,580 --> 00:20:58,780
The little girl looks pretty.

368
00:20:58,780 --> 00:20:59,700
Be careful with your hands.

369
00:21:00,140 --> 00:21:00,980
How dare you!

370
00:21:01,060 --> 00:21:02,500
Come and play with me.

371
00:21:02,540 --> 00:21:03,300
Go away.

372
00:21:04,260 --> 00:21:05,260
This is my wife.

373
00:21:05,700 --> 00:21:06,260
Beat him.

374
00:21:06,260 --> 00:21:07,540
Do you see the token? Take him.

375
00:21:07,580 --> 00:21:08,300
All right, let's go.

376
00:21:08,300 --> 00:21:09,060
Beat him.

377
00:21:09,980 --> 00:21:10,780
Knock it off.

378
00:21:11,580 --> 00:21:12,380
Seriously.

379
00:21:12,460 --> 00:21:13,300
My wife.

380
00:21:15,100 --> 00:21:16,300
This is my wife.

381
00:21:17,260 --> 00:21:18,060
My wife.

382
00:21:23,780 --> 00:21:26,060
Are you done with the cuddle?

383
00:21:28,940 --> 00:21:30,700
Don't you forget what we're here for.

384
00:21:33,100 --> 00:21:34,100
To protect my wife.

385
00:21:39,700 --> 00:21:41,020
What are we doing here?

386
00:21:42,540 --> 00:21:43,540
Looking for Shangguan Ya.

387
00:21:44,020 --> 00:21:45,340
Yeah, where is she?

388
00:21:47,500 --> 00:21:50,540
Make your decision now.

389
00:21:51,060 --> 00:21:52,540
Big, big.

390
00:21:55,020 --> 00:21:57,580
Everything you buy today is on me.

391
00:21:57,580 --> 00:22:00,060
Everyone, eat and drink as you please.

392
00:22:00,300 --> 00:22:01,100
Shangguan Ya?

393
00:22:12,940 --> 00:22:15,260
Enough with the food. Here's silver.

394
00:22:16,620 --> 00:22:19,100
Bravo.

395
00:22:19,740 --> 00:22:21,300
Take the money. Take the money.

396
00:22:21,540 --> 00:22:22,780
Shangguan Ya, stop.

397
00:22:23,100 --> 00:22:23,780
Slow down.

398
00:22:24,060 --> 00:22:24,580
Move. Move.

399
00:22:24,580 --> 00:22:25,060
Be careful.

400
00:22:25,060 --> 00:22:26,060
Thank you. Thank you.

401
00:22:26,060 --> 00:22:27,740
Make way. Move.

402
00:22:29,860 --> 00:22:30,580
No.

403
00:22:30,580 --> 00:22:32,100
You go down there and I'll go after her.

404
00:22:32,460 --> 00:22:33,220
Be careful.

405
00:22:36,740 --> 00:22:37,740
Don't look, man.

406
00:22:37,740 --> 00:22:38,380
Stop right there.

407
00:22:38,380 --> 00:22:39,220
Make way. Move.

408
00:22:44,820 --> 00:22:46,300
Shangguan Ya, stop it.

409
00:22:46,300 --> 00:22:47,620
Why did she hit me?

410
00:22:47,620 --> 00:22:48,780
Why hit me?

411
00:22:52,100 --> 00:22:53,220
Are you blind?

412
00:23:28,020 --> 00:23:29,380
I didn't know
beauties did fall off the sky.

413
00:23:29,380 --> 00:23:31,060
Thanks. You're very kind.

414
00:23:32,700 --> 00:23:34,700
Take this, man.

415
00:23:34,700 --> 00:23:36,380
I just won them. To give you good luck.

416
00:23:36,380 --> 00:23:37,860
Don't tell people you've seen me.

417
00:23:38,940 --> 00:23:40,100
What? Not enough?

418
00:23:40,780 --> 00:23:42,100
Did you just see a girl

419
00:23:42,100 --> 00:23:43,340
dressed as a man?

420
00:23:43,740 --> 00:23:44,380
I didn't.

421
00:23:45,060 --> 00:23:47,220
Have a look here.

422
00:23:56,380 --> 00:23:58,500
Take a look. It's cheap.

423
00:24:08,340 --> 00:24:09,300
First Young Master Su?

424
00:24:11,980 --> 00:24:13,980
Your Highness, why are you here?

425
00:24:14,620 --> 00:24:15,540
Did you see a girl

426
00:24:15,540 --> 00:24:16,620
dressed as a man?

427
00:24:21,380 --> 00:24:22,220
I did.

428
00:24:22,740 --> 00:24:23,780
She went that way.

429
00:24:24,540 --> 00:24:26,700
Wait. I'll come down. Pick me up.

430
00:24:32,100 --> 00:24:32,820
Li Rong?

431
00:24:39,500 --> 00:24:40,300
Are you okay?

432
00:24:42,620 --> 00:24:44,340
What were you yelling about?
You scared me.

433
00:24:44,820 --> 00:24:45,460
I...

434
00:24:49,180 --> 00:24:50,020
What's wrong with you?

435
00:24:50,460 --> 00:24:52,420
Inducing Her Highness
to jump from such a height?

436
00:24:52,820 --> 00:24:54,780
Can you make it up
if anything happens to her?

437
00:24:54,940 --> 00:24:55,660
I...

438
00:24:55,860 --> 00:24:57,140
You can't blame Mr. Su.

439
00:24:57,420 --> 00:24:58,580
I wanted to jump myself

440
00:24:58,580 --> 00:24:59,500
and asked him to pick me.

441
00:25:01,540 --> 00:25:02,820
She is your princess,

442
00:25:02,820 --> 00:25:04,340
How can you mess around with her?

443
00:25:04,340 --> 00:25:05,860
Mr. Pei just said yourself.

444
00:25:05,900 --> 00:25:07,340
She is my princess.

445
00:25:07,420 --> 00:25:08,460
She wanted to jump
and told me to carry her.

446
00:25:08,460 --> 00:25:09,540
How can I refuse?

447
00:25:09,620 --> 00:25:11,020
You're still making excuses, aren't you?

448
00:25:11,380 --> 00:25:12,660
I do the right things.

449
00:25:12,660 --> 00:25:13,740
Why do I need to make excuses?

450
00:25:14,100 --> 00:25:16,660
Mr. Pei, on the other hand,
why are you so angry?

451
00:25:16,660 --> 00:25:17,980
Are you worried that Her Highness

452
00:25:17,980 --> 00:25:19,140
might hurt herself,

453
00:25:19,140 --> 00:25:20,340
or did you get jealous

454
00:25:20,340 --> 00:25:21,500
because Her Highness
asked me to pick her?

455
00:25:21,500 --> 00:25:22,180
Are you questioning me here?

456
00:25:22,180 --> 00:25:23,140
Stop it.

457
00:25:23,660 --> 00:25:25,460
Let's catch up another day, Mr. Su.

458
00:25:25,620 --> 00:25:26,580
Let's find her first.

459
00:25:27,220 --> 00:25:27,860
Over there.

460
00:25:32,420 --> 00:25:33,180
In the basket.

461
00:25:37,020 --> 00:25:37,620
Are you okay?

462
00:25:37,620 --> 00:25:38,380
I'm okay.

463
00:25:43,580 --> 00:25:45,460
Mr. Pei, why did you come back?

464
00:25:46,180 --> 00:25:47,380
I want to apologise.

465
00:25:47,380 --> 00:25:48,220
That's not necessary.

466
00:25:49,140 --> 00:25:49,940
Your Highness.

467
00:25:50,660 --> 00:25:51,420
Your Highness...

468
00:25:51,420 --> 00:25:52,140
Let go.

469
00:25:55,180 --> 00:25:56,340
There's nobody in here.

470
00:25:56,820 --> 00:25:58,260
Somebody is here. Come out.

471
00:26:00,580 --> 00:26:02,220
I'll throw you in the river
if you don't get out.

472
00:26:02,220 --> 00:26:03,540
What do you want, young lady?

473
00:26:03,540 --> 00:26:04,620
Why do you touch my basket?

474
00:26:04,660 --> 00:26:05,900
Miss Shangguan, rest assured.

475
00:26:06,100 --> 00:26:08,220
We didn't come to catch you
for the Shangguan Family.

476
00:26:08,620 --> 00:26:09,220
What?

477
00:26:10,140 --> 00:26:11,580
First Young Master Su, help me.

478
00:26:14,580 --> 00:26:15,780
Why didn't you say so?

479
00:26:19,140 --> 00:26:21,780
Your Highness, my greetings.

480
00:26:28,380 --> 00:26:29,540
What His Majesty does is

481
00:26:29,540 --> 00:26:30,620
none of my business.

482
00:26:34,500 --> 00:26:37,660
He insisted on burying Qin Zhenzhen
with the empress's rites.

483
00:26:41,100 --> 00:26:43,620
You know he is always like a child.

484
00:26:44,420 --> 00:26:45,860
You are very mature.

485
00:26:46,140 --> 00:26:47,340
Don't take it too seriously.

486
00:26:49,260 --> 00:26:50,900
I never cared about His Majesty.

487
00:26:51,020 --> 00:26:52,300
There's no reason to take it seriously.

488
00:26:57,380 --> 00:26:59,300
From the moment I entered this palace,

489
00:27:00,420 --> 00:27:02,780
I was destined to go down a path
without turning back.

490
00:27:05,380 --> 00:27:06,700
It's the case for Qin Zhenzhen.

491
00:27:07,220 --> 00:27:08,380
It's the case for me.

492
00:27:09,340 --> 00:27:10,020
Ya.

493
00:27:13,780 --> 00:27:14,940
As for His Majesty...

494
00:27:17,180 --> 00:27:18,580
Since I entered the palace,

495
00:27:19,380 --> 00:27:21,580
I knew I was living
for the Shangguan Family.

496
00:27:23,500 --> 00:27:26,740
My life is like walking on thin ice.

497
00:27:29,980 --> 00:27:31,980
What else can I ask for?

498
00:27:35,940 --> 00:27:36,980
Let's talk somewhere else.

499
00:27:41,860 --> 00:27:44,180
First Young Master Su is
handsome and righteous.

500
00:27:44,180 --> 00:27:45,780
Even more so in real person.

501
00:27:47,660 --> 00:27:50,580
I've heard that Miss Shangguan was
the model for ladies of noble families.

502
00:27:50,580 --> 00:27:51,700
Seeing you in person today...

503
00:27:53,300 --> 00:27:55,460
You are really unique and special.

504
00:27:55,980 --> 00:27:57,060
Please do not laugh at me.

505
00:27:57,060 --> 00:27:58,100
I'll see you soon.

506
00:27:58,580 --> 00:27:59,380
Though...

507
00:28:00,220 --> 00:28:01,260
Miss Shangguan, rest assured.

508
00:28:01,660 --> 00:28:03,220
I took your money. I'll do my part.

509
00:28:03,420 --> 00:28:05,060
No one except us would know about this.

510
00:28:05,460 --> 00:28:06,260
First Young Master Su,

511
00:28:06,260 --> 00:28:07,500
you know customs and keep your word.

512
00:28:07,580 --> 00:28:08,500
I like you.

513
00:28:08,940 --> 00:28:10,180
Are you done yet?

514
00:28:11,820 --> 00:28:12,580
See you.

515
00:28:12,700 --> 00:28:13,300
See you.

516
00:28:15,460 --> 00:28:16,380
Mr. Shangguang,

517
00:28:17,020 --> 00:28:19,100
I sincerely ask to marry Shangguan Ya.

518
00:28:19,500 --> 00:28:20,700
Please allow me.

519
00:28:21,020 --> 00:28:22,820
Su Ronghua without the Su Family is

520
00:28:23,060 --> 00:28:24,140
nothing at all.

521
00:28:24,340 --> 00:28:25,140
Father,

522
00:28:26,980 --> 00:28:28,180
please allow it.

523
00:28:28,620 --> 00:28:29,500
Ya.

524
00:28:29,820 --> 00:28:32,060
Someone.
Shut Shangguan Ya into the backyard.

525
00:28:32,220 --> 00:28:33,660
My heart belongs to someone.

526
00:28:33,660 --> 00:28:35,580
I don't want to be the Crown Princess.

527
00:28:35,580 --> 00:28:37,340
If you leave with Su Ronghua,

528
00:28:37,340 --> 00:28:38,540
the Shangguan Family

529
00:28:38,540 --> 00:28:41,620
will be the biggest joke
of the Great Xia.

530
00:28:42,220 --> 00:28:43,580
Unexpectedly, the two of them

531
00:28:44,020 --> 00:28:46,140
met each other again in this way.

532
00:28:50,920 --> 00:28:52,350
[Jucai House]

533
00:29:02,060 --> 00:29:03,020
Miss Shangguan,

534
00:29:03,460 --> 00:29:05,860
you must be of marriageable age now.

535
00:29:07,420 --> 00:29:08,980
They've arranged a marriage for you.

536
00:29:09,020 --> 00:29:09,820
Didn't you know?

537
00:29:10,260 --> 00:29:12,020
Why do you still come to

538
00:29:12,020 --> 00:29:13,260
such a vulgar and messy place?

539
00:29:13,860 --> 00:29:14,660
I know.

540
00:29:15,140 --> 00:29:15,940
So what?

541
00:29:19,460 --> 00:29:21,700
Your marriage is with my brother,

542
00:29:21,980 --> 00:29:23,020
the Crown Prince.

543
00:29:23,460 --> 00:29:25,380
So that's what Your Highness came

544
00:29:25,380 --> 00:29:26,260
looking for me today.

545
00:29:26,540 --> 00:29:28,780
Do you want to talk to me
about the Crown Prince's marriage?

546
00:29:28,940 --> 00:29:29,700
Yes.

547
00:29:30,340 --> 00:29:33,220
I heard the Shangguan Family's choice
for the Crown Princess was

548
00:29:33,220 --> 00:29:33,860
you.

549
00:29:36,860 --> 00:29:38,340
Seeing me like this today,

550
00:29:38,460 --> 00:29:40,060
Your Highness must be very disappointed.

551
00:29:41,180 --> 00:29:42,220
But that's okay.

552
00:29:43,380 --> 00:29:45,300
If Your Highness are not happy with Ya,

553
00:29:45,300 --> 00:29:47,260
the Shangguan Family has many girls.

554
00:29:47,860 --> 00:29:48,780
At your choice.

555
00:29:52,900 --> 00:29:54,860
